## Libraries Reference

| Need | Library | Install |
|------|---------|---------|
| Morgan fingerprints | `rdkit` | `conda install -c conda-forge rdkit` |
| SAScore | `rdkit.Chem.RDConfig` (built-in contrib) | Included with RDKit |
| PAINS/Brenk filters | `rdkit.Chem.FilterCatalog` | Included with RDKit |
| SHAP | `shap` | `pip install shap` |
| Calibration | `scipy.optimize` | Included with scipy |
| Conformal prediction | `nonconformist` | `pip install nonconformist` |
| OOD detection | `rdkit.DataStructs.BulkTanimotoSimilarity` | Included with RDKit |
| Pareto analysis | `numpy` (custom logic above) | Included |
| Dashboard | `streamlit` + `plotly` | `pip install streamlit plotly` |
